# 🔍 Muntazar Classes — Complete SEO Implementation Plan

> **Domain:** muntazarclasses.in | **Deployed on:** Render (frontend) + Hostinger (DNS)  
> **Stack:** React 19 SPA (Vite) + Express backend  
> **Primary Goal:** Rank for "Hindi Medium Coaching classes near Govandi / in Govandi / near me"

---

