| Heading hierarchy | 🟡 Multiple H2s but no clear keyword mapping |
| Page-level meta for `/gallery`, `/achievements`, `/programs` | 🔴 SPA has zero meta for sub-pages |
| Internal linking strategy | 🟡 Limited cross-linking |
| Page speed optimization | 🟡 Large images, no lazy loading strategy |
| Mobile UX (Core Web Vitals) | 🟡 Needs audit |
