## 📋 Implementation Phases

---

### Phase 1: Fix Critical Meta & Schema Errors ⏱️ Day 1
**Priority: 🔴 CRITICAL**

**What I'll do (code changes):**

1. **Fix `index.html` title tag** — Add Govandi + Hindi Medium keywords
2. **Fix meta description** — Include location + USP + call-to-action
3. **Fix OG URL** — Change from `muntazarclasses.com` → `muntazarclasses.in`
4. **Fix Schema JSON-LD:**
   - Change URL to `https://muntazarclasses.in`
   - Fix phone to `+91-9221105658`
   - Fix address to actual Govandi address from footer
   - Add `LocalBusiness` type alongside `EducationalOrganization`
   - Add `geo` coordinates
   - Add `openingHours`, `priceRange`, `areaServed`

**Corrected Title:**
```
Muntazar Classes | Hindi Medium Coaching Classes in Govandi, Mumbai | SSC, HSC & Degree
```

**Corrected Meta Description:**
```
Muntazar Classes — Govandi's top coaching institute since 2008. Hindi, Urdu & English medium batches for 7th-10th SSC, 11th-12th HSC & Degree (B.Com, BAF, BMS). 95% pass rate. Book a free demo class today!
```

---

### Phase 2: Add robots.txt & sitemap.xml ⏱️ Day 1
**Priority: 🔴 CRITICAL**

**`public/robots.txt`:**
```
User-agent: *
Allow: /
Sitemap: https://muntazarclasses.in/sitemap.xml
```

**`public/sitemap.xml`:**
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">
  <url><loc>https://muntazarclasses.in/</loc><priority>1.0</priority><changefreq>weekly</changefreq></url>
  <url><loc>https://muntazarclasses.in/programs</loc><priority>0.9</priority><changefreq>monthly</changefreq></url>
  <url><loc>https://muntazarclasses.in/achievements</loc><priority>0.8</priority><changefreq>monthly</changefreq></url>
  <url><loc>https://muntazarclasses.in/gallery</loc><priority>0.7</priority><changefreq>monthly</changefreq></url>
</urlset>
```

---

### Phase 3: Add Canonical Tags & Per-Page Meta ⏱️ Day 1-2
**Priority: 🔴 CRITICAL**

**Problem:** This is an SPA — Google only sees `index.html` meta for ALL routes.

**Solution:** Install `react-helmet-async` to inject per-page `<title>`, `<meta>`, and `<link rel="canonical">`.

```bash
npm install react-helmet-async
```

**Per-page meta mapping:**

| Route | Title | Description |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| `/` | Muntazar Classes \| Hindi Medium Coaching Classes in Govandi, Mumbai | Govandi's top coaching since 2008. Hindi, Urdu & English medium. SSC, HSC & Degree. 95% pass rate. |
| `/programs` | Academic Programs \| SSC, HSC & Degree Coaching \| Muntazar Classes Govandi | Explore our School (7th-10th), College (11th-12th) & Degree programs. Hindi, Urdu & English medium batches. |
| `/achievements` | Student Results & Achievements \| Muntazar Classes Govandi | 200+ board toppers. See our students' SSC & HSC results. 95% pass rate since 2008. |
| `/gallery` | Photo Gallery \| Muntazar Classes Govandi | Explore photos from our classrooms, events, felicitations and student activities. |

