}
```

**B. FAQPage Schema (new):**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What are the fees at Muntazar Classes?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Fees vary by program..." }
    }
  ]
}
```

**C. Course Schema (new — on Programs page via Helmet):**
Each program gets a `Course` schema with `provider`, `courseMode`, etc.

**D. Review Schema (new):**
Add `Review` schema from the testimonials section.

