### Phase 8: Local SEO — Google Business Profile ⏱️ Day 3-4
**Priority: 🔴 CRITICAL (Off-site)**

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is the **#1 ranking factor** for "near me" searches. Code changes alone won't rank you — GBP is essential.

**What the client needs to do / verify:**

- [ ] **Claim & verify** Google Business Profile if not done
- [ ] **Business name:** "Muntazar Classes" (exact match)
- [ ] **Category:** Primary = "Coaching Centre", Secondary = "Tutoring Service", "Educational Institution"
- [ ] **Address:** Must match website footer + schema EXACTLY
- [ ] **Phone:** +91 92211 05658
- [ ] **Website:** https://muntazarclasses.in
- [ ] **Hours:** Mon-Sat 9:00 AM - 8:30 PM
- [ ] **Description:** Include "Hindi medium coaching classes in Govandi" naturally
- [ ] **Photos:** Upload 15-20 photos (classrooms, faculty, students, building exterior)
- [ ] **Services:** List each program (SSC, HSC Science, HSC Commerce, B.Com, BAF, BMS)
- [ ] **Attributes:** Hindi, Urdu, English languages offered
- [ ] **Posts:** Weekly GBP posts about results, admissions, events

**What I'll do in code:**
- Embed Google Maps iframe in Contact/Footer section
- Add a "Find us on Google Maps" CTA with the GBP link
- Ensure NAP on website matches GBP exactly

