### Phase 13: Monitoring & Analytics ⏱️ Day 5+
**Priority: 🟡 MEDIUM**

**A. Google Search Console:**
- [ ] Verify site ownership
- [ ] Submit sitemap.xml
- [ ] Monitor indexing status
- [ ] Track keyword impressions & clicks

**B. Google Analytics 4:**
- [ ] Add GA4 tracking script to `index.html`
- [ ] Set up conversion events (form submission, phone click, WhatsApp click)

**C. Add tracking script to `index.html`:**
```html
<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-XXXXXXXXXX"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'G-XXXXXXXXXX');
</script>
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The client needs to create a Google Analytics 4 property and provide the Measurement ID (`G-XXXXXXXXXX`).

